Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.82,0:21:20.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 快給我回過神來！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.51,0:21:38.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葵
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.34,0:21:39.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給你這個
